platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.ta.k: 恐ろしくも不思議な物語から脱出しよう

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Deciphering this game is no easy task—it feels like a metaphor. Is it a commentary on the fragile nature of trust and human connection? A scathing critique of our blind adherence to authority? Or is it just really weird? Regardless, INSIDE is an incredible journey with increasingly bizarre encounters that mix action with clever puzzle designs. The game isn’t meant to be entirely understood. It’s meant to be experienced.
